Otitis media. 16 years of pathogenesis approach.
 The authors describe 16 years of their approach to research in otitis media, their rationale, and the concepts that have evolved from their experiments and clinical work.
 The authors suggest that interest is the key to progress and not laboratory facilities.
 They extend an invitation to individuals with different backgrounds but common interest in otitis media to work together from the standpoint of pathogenesis.
